## Webhook

A webhook is a subscription from a server application to certain topics on the
viagogo platform. When an occurrence of a topic is triggered, we'll `POST` a
payload to the webhook's configured `url`.


### Properties

| **Name** | **Type** | **Description** |
| `id` | `int` | The webhook identifier |
| `name` | `string` | The name of the webhook |
| `url` | `string` | The server endpoint that will receive the webhook payload |
| `topics` | `string`[] | An array of the topics the webhook is trigger for |


